thread.title: Barry van den Berg
thread.title_full: FC-Moto.de bewertet von Barry van den Berg

author: Barry van den Berg
title: Barry van den Berg
text:
Great service and always wanting to help me the customer. I have been dealing with them for many years now and they have great products at competitive prices. I had bought motorbike trousers and the stichting let go, not a problem sent it back and I got a new pair. Their service is quick and reliable!
I would recomend them to everyone!
